#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:2
msgid "助记词管理"
msgstr "Seed Management"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:5
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:7
msgid "为了更好的保护比特派用户的财产安全，增强用户体验。比特派提供验证助记词，显示助记词功能。"
msgstr ""
"In order to protect user’s assert security preferably and enhance user’s "
"experience, Bitpie has provided Seed Verification function Seed Phrase Display function to view "
"seed."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:11
msgid "比特派助记词"
msgstr "Bitpie Seed Phrase"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:13
msgid "比特派采用HD钱包技术，12个单词（汉字）助记词相当于你的私钥，要妥善保管好，不要泄露给他人。"
msgstr ""
"Bitpie has applied HD wallet technology. The Secret Phrase showing as '12"
" words' is equivalent to your private key, which must be kept carefully "
"and could not be leak to others."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:17
msgid "比特派助记词验证"
msgstr "Bitpie Seed Phrase Verification"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:19
msgid "帮助用户再次确认助记词是否正确，避免助记词记错。"
msgstr ""
"It helps user verify whether Seed phrase is correct to prevent from "
"misremembering the wrong seed phrase."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:23
msgid "显示助记词功能"
msgstr "Seed Phrase Display Function"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:25
msgid "此功能是为了帮助比特派用户第一次进入软件，没有抄写助记词而设置。只能显示一次助记词，帮助比特派用户强化记忆。"
msgstr ""
"The function is set for user who firstly loges into Bitpie without "
"copying Seed Phrase. Seed Phrase is only shown once to help user strength"
" the memory."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:27
msgid "我已抄好－输入助记词验证"
msgstr "Copied it well---Input Seed Phrase to verify"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:32
msgid "保存助记词"
msgstr "Seed Preservation"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:35
msgid "1.首次打开比特派后，你将会看到如下界面"
msgstr "1.The first time you log in Bitpie, you will see the following interface."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:44
msgid "2.认真阅读”特别提示“后，点击”开始使用“按钮"
msgstr ""
"2.After reading 'Special Reminder' carefully, you click the 'Get Started'"
" button."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:54
msgid ""
"3.请按顺序抄下这些单词，如果条件允许，可以点左上方开启打印模式，打印（复印）一份你的助记词。或者也可以认真抄写你的助记词。"
"点击”我已抄好，去验证“按钮，在新页面通过选择输入抄写的单词（汉字）.为了验证你是否抄写正确，进入比特派后，可以到我——钱包设置——验证助记词，输入备份的单词，检验是否抄写正确。"
msgstr ""
"3.Please copy these words in order, if the conditions permit, you can "
"click the top left button to open the print mode for printing your seed. "
"After clicking “Copied it well” button, you can input the copied "
"characters (words) in a new interface. In order to verify whether the "
"copied characters are correct, you can access to Me-Settings—Seed "
"Verification and input those to check after activating Bitpie."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:57
msgid "大家在使用时，要认真阅读比特派的操作提示，尤其是像注册时候要备份助记词（12个单词或汉字），不要出现卸载比特派或者恢复出厂设置等高危行为。"
msgstr ""
"When you use Bitpie, please read Operation Reminder of Bitpie earnestly "
"especially like backing up seed (12 words) at the important registration "
"time to avoid the high-risk behaviour including uninstall Bitpie, restore"
" Factory Defaults."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:59
msgid "点击“我已抄好”按钮，进入下一步。"
msgstr "Clicking “Copied it well” button into next step."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:64
msgid "恢复助记词"
msgstr "Seed Recovery"

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:66
msgid "通过抄写的助记词进行恢复"
msgstr "1.Seed Recovery by copying it well."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:68
msgid "恢复助记词就是恢复你之前已注册的比特派钱包和账户，需要使用之前备份好的助记词（12个单词或汉字）。从左到右，从上到下，一个一个输入哦，如果输入某个字错误，点击那个字可修改。"
msgstr ""
"Seed Recovery is to recover your previously registered wallet and account"
" of Bitpie. It requires you input the copied seed (12 Words) one by one "
"from left to right, upside and underside. If input a wrong word, you can "
"click it to delete or replace."

#: ../../RegisterAndRecover/index.rst:76
msgid "在注册或者恢复完成之后，接下来你会看到让你设置（重置）pin密码的界面，像你手机的密码一样，让钱包更加安全。要牢记并且设置好pin密码，因为你在使用比特派的时候会经常用到的。每次重新恢复钱包后，可以重置一次新的pin密码。"
msgstr ""
"After finishing registration or recovery, you will see an interface "
"letting you reset pin password (like phone’s password) which make your "
"wallet more secure. Please keep it in mind and set pin password well. "
"Each time when recover your wallet, you can reset a new pin password."